OL,4,CColleges need extra #570m due to rise
OL,5,Cin students - think tank
OL,6, Colleges and sixth forms in England
OL,7, need an extra #570m to keep pace with
OL,8, the rising number of students, says the
OL,9, Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS).
OL,11,FThe rise in numbers of older teenagers,
OL,12,Fand higher GCSE grades, is set to push
OL,13,Fup college numbers.
OL,15,FThe IFS says funding for 16-to-18
OL,16,Flearning fell in real terms by 11% in
OL,17,Fcolleges and 25% in schools since 2010.
OL,19,FThe government says it has announced an
OL,20,Fextra #291m for 2021-22 in addition to
OL,21,Fa #400m increase in the previous year.
